---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { pageSeo } from '../seo/page-config';

const seo = pageSeo.docs;
const releaseUrl = 'https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases';
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary px-4 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <header class="mx-auto mb-14 max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-balance font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary md:text-5xl">
          Docs: install, encrypt, decrypt, verify
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Minimal command guide for the current Moaiy workflow on macOS.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/70 p-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary">1. Download from official channel</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Use GitHub Releases as the source of truth.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> open https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases</div>
          </div>
          <a
            href={releaseUrl}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            data-analytics-event="download_click"
            class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-accent-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-bg-primary transition-colors hover:bg-accent-secondary"
          >
            Open Releases
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/70 p-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary">2. Generate a key pair</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Create keys once, then back up your private key offline.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy key generate</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/70 p-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary">3. Encrypt data</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Use recipient mode or password mode depending on your case.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy encrypt secret.txt --recipient alice@example.com</div>
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy encrypt secret.txt --password</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/70 p-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary">4. Decrypt and verify</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Decrypt trusted artifacts and verify checksums before install.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy decrypt secret.txt.gpg</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/verification/" class="mt-4 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-accent-primary hover:underline">Read verification guide</a>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/65 p-7 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary md:text-3xl">Build from source (optional)</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-2 rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary">
          <div>git clone https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy.git</div>
          <div>cd moaiy</div>
          <div>open Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj</div>
          <div>xcodebuild -project Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj -scheme Moaiy -destination 'platform=macOS' build</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/55 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-accent-primary/50 hover:text-accent-primary">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">README</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Overview and setup details.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/55 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-accent-primary/50 hover:text-accent-primary">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">CONTRIBUTING</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Contribution workflow and checks.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/SECURITY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/55 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-accent-primary/50 hover:text-accent-primary">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">SECURITY</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Private vulnerability reporting path.</p>
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12 space-y-3">
        <details class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/65">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">What is Moaiy?</summary>
          <p class="px-5 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Moaiy is an open-source encryption project focused on practical OpenPGP workflows.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/65">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">How do I download safely?</summary>
          <p class="px-5 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Use official GitHub Releases and verify checksums before running binaries.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-bg-secondary/65">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">Does Moaiy upload plaintext?</summary>
          <p class="px-5 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Published workflows are local-first. See the security page for current model details.</p>
        </details>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
